mierleague.com/players/331/David-Beckham/overview |title=David Beckham: Overview |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=27 September 2018}}</ref>\n*[[FA Cup]]: [[1996 FA Cup Final|1995\u201396]], [[1999 FA Cup Final|1998\u201399]]\n*[[FA Community Shield|FA Charity Shield]]: [[1996 FA Charity Shield|1996]], [[1997 FA Charity Shield|1997]]\n*[[UEFA Champions League]]: [[1999 UEFA Champions League Final|1998\u201399]]\n*[[Intercontinental Cup (football)|Intercontinental Cup]]: [[1999 Intercontinental Cup|1999]]\n\n'''Real Madrid'''<ref name=\"honours\"/>\n*[[La Liga]]: [[2006\u201307 La Liga|2006\u201307]]\n*[[Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a]]: [[2003 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|2003]]\n\n'''LA Galaxy'''<ref name=\"honours\"/>\n*[[MLS Cup]]: [[2011 Major League Soccer season|2011]], [[2012 Major League Soccer season|2012]]\n**[[Western Conference (MLS)|Western Conference (Regular Season)]]: [[2009 Major League Soccer season|2009]], [[2010 Major League Soccer season|2010]], [[2011 Major League Soccer season|2011]]\n**[[Western Conference (MLS)|Western Conference (Playoffs)]]: [[2009 Major League Soccer season|2009]], [[2011 Major League Soccer season|2011]], [[2012 Major League Soccer season|2012]]<ref name=\"Career Statistics and honours\">{{cite news|title=Career Statistics|url=https://genius.com/David-beckham-career-statistics-annotated|website=Genius.com|date=18 July 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Supporters' Shield]]: [[2010 Major League Soccer season|2010]], [[2011 Major League Soccer season|2011]]\n\n'''Paris Saint-Germain'''<ref name=\"honours\"/>\n*[[Ligue 1]]: [[2012\u201313 Ligue 1|2012\u201313]]\n\n===Individual===\n<!--LEAGUE AND FEDERATION-SANCTIONED AWARDS ONLY. No fan or magazine-voted awards. Listed in chronological order from last time won.-->\n[[File:Beckham2001award.jpg|thumb|upright|Beckham's [[2001 FIFA World Player of the Year]] runner-up trophy]]\n*[[Ballon d'Or]] \u2013 Runner-up: [[1999 Ballon d'Or|1999]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Jos\u00e9 Luis |last=Pierrend |title=European Footballer of the Year (\"Ballon d'Or\") 1999 |url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/europa-poy99.html |publisher=Rec.Sports.Soccer Statistics Foundation |accessdate=2 August 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130314042310/http://rsssf.com/miscellaneous/europa-poy99.html |archivedate=14 March 2013  }}</ref>\n*[[FIFA World Player of the Year]] \u2013 Silver Award: 1999, 2001<ref>{{cite web|first=Jos\u00e9 Luis |last=Pierrend |title=FIFA Awards |url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/fifa-awards.html |publisher=Rec.Sports.Soccer Statistics Foundation |accessdate=2 August 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112042845/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/fifa-awards.html |archivedate=12 January 2016 |df= }}</ref>\n*[[Premier League Player of the Month]]: [[1996\u201397 FA Premier League#Monthly awards|August 1996]]<ref name=PremProfile/>\n*[[Premier League]] top assist provider: [[1997\u201398 Premier League|1997\u201398]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.premierleague.com/history/1997-98|title=1997/98 Season Review|publisher=Premier League|accessdate=5 December 2018}}</ref> [[1999\u20132000 Premier League|1999\u20132000]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.premierleague.com/history/1999-00|title=1999/00 Season Review|publisher=Premier League|accessdate=5 December 2018}}</ref> [[2000\u201301 Premier League|2000\u201301]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.premierleague.com/history/2000-01|title=2000/01 Season Review|publisher=Premier League|accessdate=5 December 2018}}</ref>\n*[[PFA Young Player of the Year]]: [[1996\u201397 FA Premier League#Player and managerial awards|1996\u201397]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Gerrard named player of the year |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4935884.stm |publisher=BBC Sport (British Broadcasting Corporation) |date=23 April 2006 |accessdate=2 August 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[FWA Tribute Award]]: 2008<ref>{{cite news |title=Football writers honour United duo |url=http://www.footballwriters.co.uk/news/football-writers-honour-united-duo/ |publisher=Football Writers' Association |date=14 October 2011 |accessdate=2 August 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924014457/http://www.footballwriters.co.uk/news/football-writers-honour-united-duo/ |archive-date=24 September 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*[[Sir Matt Busby Player of the Year]]: 1996\u201397<ref>{{cite web |title=Sir Matt Busby Player of the Year Award |url=http://www.mufcinfo.com/manupag/player_of_the_year/player_of_the_year.html |publisher=MUFCInfo.com |accessdate=2 August 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[The FA England Awards|England Player of the Year]]: 2003<ref>{{cite web |title=Past Winners: David Beckham |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/news/2012/england-award-beckham-2003 |publisher=The Football Association |date=12 December 2012 |accessdate=2 August 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[European Sports Media#ESM Team of the Year|ESM Team of the Year]]: 1998\u201399\n*[[UEFA Club Footballer of the Year]]: [[1998\u201399 UEFA Champions League|1998\u201399]]<ref name=\"uefa_awards\">{{cite web |title=David Beckham |url=http://www.uefa.com/teamsandplayers/players/player=14670/profile/index.html |publisher=UEFA |date=5 March 2013 |accessdate=2 August 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Club Football Awards|UEFA Club Midfielder of the Year]]: [[1998\u201399 UEFA Champions League|1998\u201399]]<ref name=\"uefa_awards\"/>\n*[[UEFA Team of the Year]]: 2001, 2003<ref name=\"uefa_awards\"/>\n*[[Premier League 10 Seasons Awards]] (1992\u201393 to 2001\u201302):\n**[[Premier League 10 Seasons Awards#Teams of the Decade|Domestic & Overall Team of the Decade]]<ref name=\"10seasons\">{{Cite web |url=http://tenseasons.premierleague.com/ |title=10 Seasons Awards |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=2 October 2009 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20021220053545/http://tenseasons.premierleague.com/ |archivedate=20 December 2002 }}</ref>\n**[[Premier League 10 Seasons Awards#Goal of the Decade|Goal of the Decade]] (vs. Wimbledon, 17 August 1996)<ref name=\"10seasons\"/>\n*[[BBC Sports Personality of the Year]]: 2001<ref name=\"bbc_spoty\">{{cite news |title=David Beckham receives Lifetime Achievement award |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/tv_and_radio/sports_personality_of_the_year/9283138.stm |publisher=BBC Sport (British Broadcasting Corporation) |date=18 December 2010 |accessdate=2 August 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[BBC Sports Personality of the Year Lifetime Achievement Award]]: 2010<ref name=\"bbc_spoty\"/>\n*[[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]] Player of the Year: 2005\u201306\n*[[PFA Team of the Year]]: [[PFA Team of the Year (1990s)#FA Premier League 5|1996\u201397 Premier League]],<ref>{{cite book |editor-first=Barry J. |editor-last=Hugman |title=The 1997\u201398 Official PFA Footballers Factfile |year=1997 |publisher=Queen Anne Press |isbn=978-1-85291-581-0 |page=317 }}</ref> [[PFA Team of the Year (1990s)#FA Premier League 6|1997\u201398 Premier League]],<ref>{{cite book |editor-first=Barry J. |editor-last=Hugman |title=The 1998\u201399 Official PFA Footballers Factfile |year=1998 |publisher=Queen Anne Press |isbn=978-1-85291-588-9 |page=352 }}</ref> [[PFA Team of the Year (1990s)#FA Premier League 7|1998\u201399 Premier League]],<ref>{{cite book |editor-last=Hugman |editor-first=Barry J. |title=The 1999\u20132000 Official PFA Footballers Factfile |year=1999 |publisher=AFS |isbn=978-1-85291-607-7 |page=352 }}</ref> [[PFA Team of the Year (2000s)#FA Premier League|1999\u20132000 Premier League]]<ref>{{cite book |editor-last=Hugman |editor-first=Barry J. |title=The 2000\u20132001 Official PFA Footballers Factfile |year=2000 |publisher=AFS |isbn=978-1-85291-626-8 |page=384 }}</ref>\n*[[FIFA 100]]<ref>{{cite web |title=FIFA's top 100 list |url=http://www.rediff.com/sports/2004/mar/05fifa.htm |publisher=Rediff.com |accessdate=13 November 2008}}</ref>\n*[[ESPY Awards]]:\n**Best Male Soccer Player: 2004<ref name=\"autogenerated1\">{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/espy2008/postshow/index.html#/bestof/ |title=ESPYS 2008 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=13 November 2008}}</ref>\n**Best MLS Player: 2008, 2012<ref>{{cite news |title=Robbie Keane wins Best MLS Player at 2015 ESPY Awards |url=http://www.lagalaxy.com/post/2015/07/16/robbie-keane-wins-best-mls-player-2015-espy-awards |website=LAGalaxy.com |publisher=MLS |date=16 July 2015 |accessdate=2 August 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[English Football Hall of Fame]]: [[English Football Hall of Fame#2008 Inductees|2008]]<ref>{{cite web|title=David Beckham |url=http://www.nationalfootballmuseum.com/hall-of-fame/profiles/entry/david-beckham/ |publisher=National Football Museum |accessdate=2 August 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529174504/http://www.nationalfootballmuseum.com/hall-of-fame/profiles/entry/david-beckham/ |archivedate=29 May 2015 |df= }}</ref>\n*[[MLS Comeback Player of the Year Award]]: 2011<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/news/article/2011/11/14/las-beckham-named-comeback-player-year |work=MLS |title=LA's Beckham named Comeback Player of the Year |date=14 November 2011}}</ref>\n*[[Professional Footballers' Association|PFA]] Team of the Century (1997\u20132007): 2007<ref>{{cite news|title=Team of the Century: 1997\u20132007 \u2013 the Premiership's finest of the last decade |url=http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa-legends/teams-of-the-century/team-of-the-century-1997-2007 |work=GiveMeFootball.com |publisher=Give Me Football |date=5 September 2007 |accessdate=17 May 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081021032411/http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa-legends/teams-of-the-century/team-of-the-century-1997-2007 |archivedate=21 October 2008 }}</ref>\n*[[International Federation of Football History & Statistics]] (IFFHS) Legends<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iffhs.de/iffhs-has-announced-the-48-football-legend-players/|title=IFFHS announce the 48 football legend players|publisher=IFFHS|date=25 January 2016|accessdate=14 September 2016}}</ref>\n*[[UEF